#: src/main.vala:49
msgid "Compatibility tools by Valve for running Windows software on Linux."
msgstr ""
"Nástroje kompatibility od spoločnosti Valve na spúšťanie softvéru pre "
"Windows na Linuxe."

#: src/main.vala:50
msgid ""
"Steam compatibility tool for running Windows games with improvements over "
"Valve's default Proton."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam na spúšťanie hier pre Windows s vylepšeniami "
"oproti predvolenému Protonu od Valve."

#: src/main.vala:51
msgid ""
"Steam compatibility tool from the CachyOS Linux distribution for running "
"Windows games with improvements over Valve's default Proton."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam z linuxovej distribúcie CachyOS na spúšťanie "
"hier pre Windows s vylepšeními oproti predvolenému Protonu od Valve."

#: src/main.vala:52
msgid "Dawn Winery's custom Proton fork with fixes for various games :xdd:"
msgstr "Vlastný fork Protonu od Dawn Winery s opravami pre rôzne hry :xdd:"

#: src/main.vala:53
msgid ""
"Steam compatibility tool for running Windows games with improvements over "
"Valve's default Proton. By Etaash Mathamsetty adding FSR4 support and wine "
"wayland tweaks."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam na spúšťanie hier pre Windows s vylepšeniami "
"oproti predvolenému Protonu od Valve. Od autora Etaash Mathamsetty, pridáva "
"podporu FSR4 a úpravy pre wine wayland."

#: src/main.vala:54
msgid "Custom Proton build for running Windows games, based on Wine-tkg."
msgstr ""
"Vlastné zostavenie Protonu na spúšťanie hier pre Windows, založené na Wine-"
"tkg."

#: src/main.vala:55
msgid ""
"Steam compatibility tool based on Proton-GE with additional patches to "
"improve RTSP codecs for VRChat."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam založený na Proton-GE s dodatočnými opravami "
"na vylepšenie kodekov RTSP pre VRChat."

#: src/main.vala:56
msgid ""
"Luxtorpeda provides Linux-native game engines for certain Windows-only games."
msgstr ""
"Luxtorpeda poskytuje natívne linuxové herné enginy pre vybrané hry, ktoré sú "
"inak dostupné len pre Windows."

#: src/main.vala:57
msgid ""
"Steam compatibility tool for running adventure games using ScummVM for Linux."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam na spúšťanie adventúr pomocou ScummVM pre "
"Linux."

#: src/main.vala:58
msgid "Steam compatibility tool for running DOS games using DOSBox for Linux."
msgstr ""
"Nástroj kompatibility pre Steam na spúšťanie DOS hier pomocou DOSBoxu pre "
"Linux."

#: src/main.vala:59
msgid "Compatibility tools for running Windows software on Linux."
msgstr "Nástroje kompatibility na spúšťanie softvéru pre Windows na Linuxe."

#: src/main.vala:60
msgid "Wine build compiled from the official WineHQ sources."
msgstr "Zostavenie Wine skompilované z oficiálnych zdrojov WineHQ."

#: src/main.vala:61
msgid "Wine build with the Staging patchset."
msgstr "Zostavenie Wine so sadou opráv Staging."

#: src/main.vala:62
msgid "Wine build with the Staging patchset and many other useful patches."
msgstr ""
"Zostavenie Wine so sadou opráv Staging a mnohými ďalšími užitočnými opravami."

#: src/main.vala:63
msgid "Wine build modified by Valve and other contributors."
msgstr "Zostavenie Wine upravené spoločnosťou Valve a ďalšími prispievateľmi."

#: src/main.vala:64
msgid "Vulkan-based implementation of Direct3D 8, 9, 10 and 11 for Linux/Wine."
msgstr ""
"Implementácia Direct3D 8, 9, 10 a 11 pre Linux/Wine založená na grafickom "
"rozhraní Vulkan."

#: src/main.vala:65
#, fuzzy
msgid "DXVK builds that work with pre-Vulkan 1.3 versions."
